{"type":"message","id":"ec3e53f8","parentId":"b4280735","timestamp":"2026-03-13T02:33:04.208Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想创建一个 skill，并询问是否有相关的 skills 可以使用。他们还希望了解热度靠前的 skills 作为参考。\n\n让我检查可用的 skills 列表。从 injected skills 中，我看到有：\n1. `skill-creator` - 专门用于创建 skills 的指南\n2. `find-skills` - 帮助用户发现和安装 skills\n\n这两个都很相关。`skill-creator` 是最直接匹配的，因为它专门用于\"创建新 skill 或更新现有 skill\"。\n\n按照 skills 的使用规范：\n- 如果只有一个 skill 明确适用，就读取它的 SKILL.md 然后遵循\n- 如果多个可能适用，选择最具体的那个\n\n这里 `skill-creator` 是最具体匹配的，应该读取它。\n\n另外，用户还想了解\"热度靠前的 skills\"。这可能需要：\n1. 使用 `find-skills` skill 来搜索\n2. 或者访问 ClawHub 网站\n\n让我先读取 `skill-creator` 的 SKILL.md，然后看看是否需要使用 `find-skills` 来查找热门 skills。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我来帮你查看创建 skill 相关的资源。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e0fcc08e027b4298bbd0bec5","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.agents/skills/skill-creator-0.1.0/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":11789,"output":256,"cacheRead":4800,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16845,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773369171606}}
