{"type":"message","id":"e0fde477","parentId":"c3f75f48","timestamp":"2026-03-13T02:33:41.927Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，clawhub search 遇到了 rate limit。让我尝试其他方式：\n\n1. 可以访问 ClawHub 网站查看热门 skills\n2. 或者使用 curl 直接访问 ClawHub API\n3. 或者列出一些已知的、在 skills 列表中我看到的热门 skills\n\n从 available_skills 列表中，我可以看到很多有趣的 skills。让我整理一下，并尝试使用 clawhub 的其他命令来获取热门列表。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e1a99e6209054e6583c7d706","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"clawhub --help 2>&1 | grep -A 30 \"Commands:\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_98ebd38cd8f94637b1261690","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s \"https://clawhub.com/api/skills?sort=popular&limit=10\" 2>/dev/null | head -100"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1311,"output":158,"cacheRead":17280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18749,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773369214046}}
{"type":"message","id":"3ee23726","parentId":"e0fde477","timestamp":"2026-03-13T02:33:42.250Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_e1a99e6209054e6583c7d706","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Commands:\n  login [options]                         Log in (opens browser or stores token)\n  logout                                  Remove stored token\n  whoami                                  Validate token\n  auth                                    Authentication commands\n  search [options] <query...>             Vector search skills\n  install [options] <slug>                Install into <dir>/<slug>\n  update [options] [slug]                 Update installed skills\n  uninstall [options] <slug>              Uninstall a skill\n  list                                    List installed skills (from lockfile)\n  explore [options]                       Browse latest updated skills from the registry\n  inspect [options] <slug>                Fetch skill metadata and files without installing\n  publish [options] <path>                Publish skill from folder\n  delete [options] <slug>                 Soft-delete a skill (moderator/admin only)\n  hide [options] <slug>                   Hide a skill (moderator/admin only)\n  undelete [options] <slug>               Restore a hidden skill (moderator/admin only)\n  unhide [options] <slug>                 Unhide a skill (moderator/admin only)\n  ban-user [options] <handleOrId>         Ban a user and delete owned skills (moderator/admin only)\n  set-role [options] <handleOrId> <role>  Change a user role (admin only)\n  star [options] <slug>                   Add a skill to your highlights\n  unstar [options] <slug>                 Remove a skill from your highlights\n  sync [options]                          Scan local skills and publish new/updated ones\n\nEnv:\n  CLAWHUB_SITE\n  CLAWHUB_REGISTRY\n  CLAWHUB_WORKDIR\n  (CLAWDHUB_* supported)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":321,"aggregated":"Commands:\n  login [options]                         Log in (opens browser or stores token)\n  logout                                  Remove stored token\n  whoami                                  Validate token\n  auth                                    Authentication commands\n  search [options] <query...>             Vector search skills\n  install [options] <slug>                Install into <dir>/<slug>\n  update [options] [slug]                 Update installed skills\n  uninstall [options] <slug>              Uninstall a skill\n  list                                    List installed skills (from lockfile)\n  explore [options]                       Browse latest updated skills from the registry\n  inspect [options] <slug>                Fetch skill metadata and files without installing\n  publish [options] <path>                Publish skill from folder\n  delete [options] <slug>                 Soft-delete a skill (moderator/admin only)\n  hide [options] <slug>                   Hide a skill (moderator/admin only)\n  undelete [options] <slug>               Restore a hidden skill (moderator/admin only)\n  unhide [options] <slug>                 Unhide a skill (moderator/admin only)\n  ban-user [options] <handleOrId>         Ban a user and delete owned skills (moderator/admin only)\n  set-role [options] <handleOrId> <role>  Change a user role (admin only)\n  star [options] <slug>                   Add a skill to your highlights\n  unstar [options] <slug>                 Remove a skill from your highlights\n  sync [options]                          Scan local skills and publish new/updated ones\n\nEnv:\n  CLAWHUB_SITE\n  CLAWHUB_REGISTRY\n  CLAWHUB_WORKDIR\n  (CLAWDHUB_* supported)","cwd":"/Users/yanxin/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773369222249}}
