{"type":"message","id":"2f2b563a","parentId":"0ca4c3c5","timestamp":"2026-03-13T02:58:48.542Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我无法直接读取 brainstorming skill。让我直接分析需求并设计方案。\n\n根据 autoglm-browser-agent 的文档，我现在理解了工作流程：\n1. 调用 browser_subagent 执行浏览器任务\n2. 如果遇到登录/验证码等需要人工交互的场景，会返回 `[INTERACT_REQUIRED]`\n3. 此时告知用户手动操作\n4. 用户完成后，带 session_id 恢复任务\n\n现在让我设计一个完整的方案：\n\n方案一：完全依赖 browser_subagent\n- 优点：简单，一次性完成\n- 缺点：可能难以精确控制每个细节（如解密按钮的点击）\n\n方案二：分步执行\n- 优点：可以精确控制每个步骤\n- 缺点：需要多次调用，管理复杂\n\n方案三：混合模式\n- 使用 browser_subagent 完成浏览器操作\n- 将结果返回给我，我负责保存CSV\n\n我认为方案三最合适。让我先检查一下是否需要读取配置文件（信任模式）：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3dbf292c0ec040a28431b7ff","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw-autoclaw/config.json 2>/dev/null || echo \"config not found\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_db54c0a13fc145aea4be3662","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw-autoclaw/session_pool.json 2>/dev/null || echo \"session_pool not found\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":553,"output":274,"cacheRead":26368,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27195,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773370712513}}
