{"type":"message","id":"e78da45a","parentId":"9fe20306","timestamp":"2026-03-13T03:03:29.327Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来 autoglm-browser-agent 的 MCP server 有问题，Python 库加载失败。这是 macOS 安全限制的问题。\n\n让我尝试另一个方案：使用其他浏览器自动化工具，比如 Playwright 或 Puppeteer。\n\n或者我可以直接用 Python + Playwright 来实现这个功能，创建一个独立的脚本。\n\n让我看看用户系统中是否有 playwright 或其他浏览器自动化工具。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1bfc2260639a481dab57fdeb","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"which playwright && playwright --version || echo \"playwright not found\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_aa01f76d506a439c9f998396","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"import playwright; print('playwright installed')\" 2>&1 || echo \"playwright not in python\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":25721,"output":131,"cacheRead":4736,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30588,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773370997205}}
